cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Arabic / Oil & Gas LLM Evaluation Benchmark"
message: "If you use this benchmark in research or model releases, please cite as below."
type: dataset
authors:
  - family-names: Albasha
    given-names: Hossain
    email: Albasha.Hossain@gmail.com
    affiliation: Independent
repository-code: "https://github.com/Hossain-Albasha/arabic-og-llm-eval"
abstract: >-
  A small, opinionated evaluation benchmark and harness for testing how well
  large language models handle bilingual Arabic / English Oil & Gas technical
  content. Targets failure modes that surface in production AR/EN industrial
  deployments (terminology recall, code-switching, diacritization sensitivity,
  hallucinated proper nouns) which standard benchmarks do not probe.
keywords:
  - llm-evaluation
  - benchmark
  - arabic-nlp
  - bilingual
  - oil-and-gas
  - industrial-ai
